(12900, '2008-02-15', 'Audiosurf Update Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1450\" style=\"display: ;\">
<p>Updates to Audiosurf have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Audiosurf</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Refreshes track graphics after a minimize<br/><li>Spotlight finish now requires an elite character<br/><li>Performance improvements<br/></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
