(12900, '2008-03-07', 'Audiosurf Update Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1475\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Updates to Audiosurf have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Audiosurf</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Added separate volume controls for menu music, game music, and sound effects<br/><li>Added new Mono Pro vehicle with jump fins (was in previous update)<br/><li>Play Double Vision with X360 controller and Mouse (or X360 controller only)<br/><li>Added \"resend score\" button in the event of a timeout<br/><li>Increased score submitting timeout duration to 22 seconds<br/><li>\"Sharp corners\" tweak now applies to ironmode only</li></li></li></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
